%F A021368 From _Chai Wah Wu_, Oct 03 2016: (Start)
%F A021368 a(n) = a(n-1) - a(n-3) + a(n-4) for n > 5.
%F A021368 G.f.: x^2*(2 + 5*x - 3*x^2 + 5*x^3)/(1 - x + x^3 - x^4). (End)
%e A021368 0.00274725274725274725274725274725274725274725274725274725274725274725274725....
